{"tid":1776931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警被蒙面人施襲受傷　14歲少女涉行為不檢被捕","createTime":"2019-12-10T01:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T13:58:02.000Z","uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"abcc68a1f2a8c09a8ae363e2d78a1f70c6ca0480","tid":1776931,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"警方昨日在大埔拘捕一名14歲少女，涉嫌公眾地方行為不檢。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨日下午5時許，警方說有大約5名蒙面人，在太和路以垃圾筒及竹枝堵路，一名休班警員尾隨堵路者，去到普益街及寶鄉街交界，警員被蒙面人用手襲擊，面部受傷，其後拘捕一名14歲少女。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列作傷人及公眾地方行為不檢，並強烈譴責針對休班警員的施襲行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496848-20191210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496848-20191210.htm&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=92769876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496848-20191210.htm&h=23941db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496848-20191210.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c862fd0f35b0d8c69f2129eb054dae2c17aebe62","tid":1776931,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:21:36.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日一致通過啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"77041effe7236c00680cd7e15cd424233b7939d6","tid":1776931,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:28:39.000Z","msg":"休班狗定便衣狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb059b4db5d